metadata.name: But their problems
metadata.description:
because at this time, endless cold already wrapped their body, they can feel the blood stopped flowing inside the body, the heart gradually become slow, then they can only look at the coming of death's shadow to despair at his side -- and then quietly swallowed their soul.



"Bang!!"



It was only when the last touch of soul light disappeared that Fang Zheng fell to his knees. The armor of his body melted away, and the mysterious and terrible sword in his hand melted into the cold wind and vanished into the air. And above him, the great apparition watched him motionless, then melted into the darkness and disappeared.



"Ah......... Ha......"
